{
  "title": {
    "en": "Quick start checklist"
  },
  "description": {
    "en": "The shortest path to your first useful Oviond report."
  },
  "content": {
    "en": {
      "type": "doc",
      "content": [
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "Use this checklist when you are setting up Oviond for the first time."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "bulletList",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Create or join your agency account."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Add your first client."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Connect at least one data source for that client."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Create a report or dashboard."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Add widgets that use the connected data source."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "listItem",
              "content": [
                {
                  "type": "paragraph",
                  "content": [
                    {
                      "type": "text",
                      "text": "Share the report with your client or test an automation."
                    }
                  ]
                }
              ]
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "type": "paragraph",
          "content": [
            {
              "type": "text",
              "text": "If you get stuck, start by checking whether the client has a connected data source and whether the widget date range contains data."
            }
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  },
  "plainContent": {
    "en": "Use this checklist when you are setting up Oviond for the first time.\n\n*   Create or join your agency account.\n    \n*   Add your first client.\n    \n*   Connect at least one data source for that client.\n    \n*   Create a report or dashboard.\n    \n*   Add widgets that use the connected data source.\n    \n*   Share the report with your client or test an automation.\n    \n\nIf you get stuck, start by checking whether the client has a connected data source and whether the widget date range contains data."
  },
